shared_text:
Kaneland Athletics-Activities
April 16 at 3:18 PM Â·

Senior Recognition:
In an effort to keep looking forward, we will be joining several of our I8 Conference Schools as well as schools across the state by recognizing our Seniors on Friday Nights from 8:00 pm - 8:20 pm (20:20) by turning on the Stadium Lights for '20' Minutes (#BeTheLight). I encourage you to help spread the word that we will be asking the Kaneland Community to do the same at their homes by turning on their front porch lights for '20' minutes during the same time. We do not want the community to gather at school but if they drive by, we encourage them to stay in their cars and not to park. This will be Kaneland's continued effort to join other schools to symbolically recognize those seniors who are certainly having a different kind of Senior Spring.

Booster Members, Parents and Friends, we are in need of your help! We are looking for a new President and Secretary for next years executive board. Our long tenured Co-Presidents Joel Redman and Robin Redman are moving on to other horizons beginning next year. We would love for you to start attending our meetings and join the Boosters to help guide us into the 2021 school year.
